        "question": "বিম্বের রৈখিক বিবর্ধন ($m$) কত?",
        "mark": 3
      }
    ],
    "solution": "<p><strong>ক)</strong> $P = \\frac{1}{f} = \\frac{1}{0.1} = 10$ Dioptre (D)।</p><p><strong>খ)</strong> $\\frac{1}{v} = \\frac{1}{f} - \\frac{1}{u} = \\frac{1}{10} - \\frac{1}{15} = \\frac{3-2}{30} = \\frac{1}{30} \\implies v = 30\\text{ cm}$।</p><p><strong>গ)</strong> যেহেতু $v$ ধনাত্মক, বিম্বটি বাস্তব।</p><p><strong>ঘ)</strong> $m = |-\\frac{v}{u}| = \\frac{30}{15} = 2$।</p>"
  },
